16. fxe6! { Mission accomplished. } Bxe6 ( 16...fxe6 $4 { Loses to } 17.Qf7+ $18 ) 
17. Nf5 {[%cal Gf5d6][%csl Rd6]} Bxf5 
18. gxf5 $14  { Black still needs to be quite precise to not end up in a lost position, but even with correct play, the situation is not equal anymore. } ( 18.gxf5 { Black can try } 18...Naxb3 19.axb3 Ne4 20.c4 $5 { and the position remains much better for White. } ) *

